  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your tandoor to around 350°F.",
    "In a small bowl, mix the olive oil with the chopped fresh herbs. Set aside.",
    "In another bowl, combine the pistachio paste, coconut milk, almond flour, cornstarch, turmeric powder, salt, and ground cumin. Mix well until smooth.",
    "Pour the mixture into the tandoor and swirl it around to coat evenly with the oil and herbs.",
    "Close the tandoor and cook for about 20-30 minutes or until the crust is golden brown.",
    "Serve hot as a dessert."
